I try to keep stock what is practical and add what is needed, (thanks for
the 9-pin replacement circuit). Since my 67 SC is tooling around with
non-standard windshield wiper blades adapted to the original arms, turn
signal 9-pin modification, and a late model 71 DP engine, the one thing that
remains in common with the rest of the owners is that big smile and wave
when you pass me on the road!

